summary: An Ordinance granting to Ed Sweeney, authority and permission to improve, by grading, East Blain Street, from Tenth Avenue North to Eleventh Avenue North; East Howe Street, from Tenth Avenue North to Eleventh Avenue North, and Eleventh Avenue North, from the South line of Broadway Second Addition to the City of Seattle to East Howe Street, all in the City of Seattle, at his own proper cost and expense.
